      "role": "user",
      "content": "I don't know, acetaminophen never really works for my headaches... it's like it does nothing. Ibuprofen always hits the spot quickly. I've taken it before without any issues, so is it really that dangerous to just take one or two and be done with it? It shouldn't be a big deal for just a single dose, right?",
